application - package application
This is the root package for most, if not all, backend code.
application.controller - package application.controller
This package contains classes that are to be loaded as spring MVC controllers.
application.data - package application.data
 
application.data.DTO - package application.data.DTO
web-facing structured data (usually JSON/XML documents) is generated at application.controllercontroller classes from POJO classes defined here.
application.data.entity - package application.data.entity
internal data for the application is stored as java EE entity beans, described in this package as POJOS with private fields and public getter/setters.
application.data.repository - package application.data.repository
this package contains classes using spring data to power internal database CRUD operations and persistance.
application.service - package application.service
Overall business logic starts through classes located here, consisting mostly of decision-making, CRUD operations and data validation.
